Description_lang: The Jailer marks a player for death, inflicting $s1 Shadow damage every $t1 sec, growing in intensity over $d and killing the player upon expiration.Upon removal, the player releases dark energy at nearby locations that apply $@spellname363748 to players struck. If the energy fails to hit at least one player, $@spellname363748 is applied to all players.Gaining two applications of $@spellname363748 kills players instantly.
